Package org.reactivestreams.utils.spi

Interface Stage

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Stage.Inlet, Stage.Outlet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Stage.Collect, Stage.Failed, Stage.Filter, Stage.FindFirst, Stage.FlatMap, Stage.FlatMapCompletionStage, Stage.FlatMapIterable, Stage.ForEach, Stage.Map, Stage.Of, Stage.Processor, Stage.Publisher, Stage.Subscriber, Stage.TakeWhile

    public interface Stage
    A stage of a Reactive Streams graph.

    A Reactive Streams engine will walk a graph of stages to produce Stage.Publisher, Stage.Subscriber and Stage.Processor instances that handle the stream according to the sequence of stages.
